reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 13, 2023
reviews.reviewText: I was expecting to see more like a stone cut with less shine but it is a very nice set for the price! I’m a country gal ! This set will look really nice with my country styles!!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 30, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Purchase two... one for you and one for gift
reviews.reviewText: Cannot go wrong for the $$. Usually, when you order a necklace with earrings set, the earrings are so tiny you can hardly see them...not so with this set. Very nice...the necklace adjusts in length. Bought this to wear with a western dress. The necklace chain could be more sturdy but for the price, I'll replace the chain myself. Bought a second set for a friend. Looks and feels more expensive than it is.... except for the chain.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 22, 2022
reviews.reviewText: I liked the color of the stone and the style.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 26, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Expect to be Impressed - These are stunning!
reviews.reviewText: I was absolutely delighted and very impressed with how truly beautiful these are when they arrived. I bought these as a gift for my sister. She took the on a trip to Europe which included boats down rivers to several countries - a lot of small towns, sightseeing, dress up dinners. She found them to be versatile and always received complements. I was a bit nervous because she's usually a yellow gold person but let's face it Turquoise is rarely - if ever in yellow gold settings. The stone is best complimented in silver and this set being so beautiful she loves them!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 19, 2019
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Looks great even if it feels cheap, I hate that description but ...
reviews.reviewText: So beautiful but it feels cheap. I hate using that description but it doesn’t feel strong and heavy like solid metal and stone usually does. I have to give 5 stars though because of how really good it looks. When I first took it out of its packaging I was worried but putting it on it doesn’t really matter because you can’t even tell it wasn’t an expensive set! It has an antique- esk look and it’s not heavy so it doesn’t weigh down on my ears or feel super heavy, it’s actually a plus.Additional information:The plastic metal was not formed well because I cut me but it’s only on the necklace, the earrings are perfect.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on March 15, 2021
reviews.reviewText: So I bought these earrings before and lost one about three years ago. I really liked them so, despite the low cost, it was a bummer. I was thrilled to find this set again and went ahead and bought them. Normally I'd just give these a good review for being pretty and go on with my life, and you CAN go ahead and consider this a good review... with a caveat. I would be remiss if I didn't ding the seller / manufacturer over the fact that the earrings were attached to the hook backwards. I either have to take time out of my life to re-hook them or wear them with the hook facing out instead of in. :/
